translations: 为……描眉（eyebrow 的第三人称单数）

sentences.sentence: You've plucked your eyebrows at last!
Eyebrows can be tinted with the same dye.
sentences.translation: 眉毛可淡淡地染成相同的颜色。

sentences.sentence: The strong, dark eyebrows give his face an oddly menacing look.
sentences.translation: 两道又浓又黑的眉毛给他的脸一种异常吓人的神情。
